# Type Checking
enforce strict null checks
require explicit return types
prevent implicit any usage
enforce literal types
require discriminated unions
enforce tagged templates

# Error Prevention
enforce exhaustive checks
require error boundaries
prevent unchecked indexing
enforce const assertions
require explicit overrides
prevent type widening

# Code Organization
enforce barrel patterns
require feature folders
enforce domain separation
implement type grouping
require interface segregation
enforce naming conventions

# Anti-Patterns
prevent type assertion
avoid type casting
prevent any usage
avoid namespace merging
prevent interface merging
enforce single responsibility